{"tid":1512814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美銀：人民幣年底跌至7.5","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:21:37.000Z","uid":56533,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90a92e0dbe86bed79ebc68b780ff24ce54f810c0","tid":1512814,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】中國外交部昨日繼續否認美國官員指，雙方近日曾就貿易問題通電話，貿易戰未有緩和的跡象，<span style=\"color: red;\">人民幣匯率昨日再創11年以來新低。</span>人民銀行昨公布中間價報7.081，比上個交易日上升240點子（1元等於1萬點子），路透估算逆周期因子推升達499點子，但亦無阻人民幣開市走弱。美銀美林下調人民幣匯率預期，至今年底將跌至7.5。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚低見7.1691 離岸拆息急升<br />\n在岸人民幣走勢偏低，至傍晚最多低見7.1691，下跌近200點子，不過香港人民幣拆息近期急升，隔夜拆息昨升62點子（1厘等於100點子）至4.69厘，有助遏止離岸價下跌，加上美元回調，人民幣收窄跌幅，截至晚上10時，在岸價報7.1595，下跌92點子，離岸價報7.1602，上升78點子。交易員指，由於外部環境惡化，人民幣貶值壓力增加，短期內仍需消化貿易戰貶值影響，不過現時監管當局似乎無意強行扭轉人民幣跌勢。<br />\n<br />\n美銀美林再發報告，將人民幣年底目標由7.3降至7.5，為近三周以來第二次下調。該行審視美國上調關稅對人民幣的影響，若人行以匯率抵銷關稅影響，以12月美國將對3000億美元中國貨品徵收15%關稅計算，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人民幣最多貶至7.66</strong></span>，不過中國亦會向美國徵收關稅，可減少人民幣需貶值的影響。美銀美林認為，人民幣貶值仍然採取漸進方式進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190828/s00004/1566930205205/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B37-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190828%2Fs00004%2F1566930205205%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%258A%2580-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2587%25B37-5&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=0a09cefa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190828%2Fs00004%2F1566930205205%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%258A%2580-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%2595%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2587%25B37-5&h=f334c6ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190828/s00004/1566930205205/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B37-5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daab8aa268f1f21dc2c7f7d2ac04c3316d7d818","tid":1512814,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd705157fed5ec8da4cc2c816d8655530dd1da1","tid":1512814,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ff2ac5b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=962a901d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=612a7dd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"441cf565454986c4ca7087f40b3c827925085306","tid":1512814,"uid":197640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"一對一之後入面好快會再收番港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca1531e407bbc586456f94b5b784db864bfc613","tid":1512814,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"